  "bodyHtml": "<head>\n<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=Windows-1252\">\n<style type=\"text/css\" style=\"display:none;\"> P {margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;} </style>\n</head>\n<body dir=\"ltr\">\n<div class=\"elementToProof\" style=\"font-family: Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\nTere!</div>\n<div class=\"elementToProof\" style=\"font-family: Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\n<br>\n</div>\n<div class=\"elementToProof\" style=\"font-family: Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\nTänan, et märkisite ära puudujäägi boti-vastaste meetmete tuvastuses!</div>\n<div class=\"elementToProof\" style=\"font-family: Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\n<br>\n</div>\n<div class=\"elementToProof\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-family: Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\nVastavalt Euroopa Liidu isikuandmete kaitse üldmäärusele (GDPR) peab isikuandmete töötlemiseks olema seaduslik alus (<a href=\"https://eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-content/ET/TXT/?uri=CELEX:32016R0679#art_6\" id=\"OWAcab88e51-c830-a2ca-7116-6d15d13fe700\" class=\"OWAAutoLink\" style=\"margin: 0px;\">Artikkel\n 6</a>). Millisel alusel edastate/avalikustate kooliga seotuse (s.t. kasutaja olemasolu) võõrastele&nbsp;osapooltele?</div>\n<div class=\"elementToProof\" style=\"font-family: Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\n<br>\nKas saaksite täpsustada, millistes \"teatud olukordades\" ei ole konto eksisteerimise kohta käiva info kättesaadavus andmeleke? Kindlasti võib seda teada kooli juhtkond, aga kas pidasite ka silmas, et kooliga mitteseotud pooled võivad kontode olemasolu kontrollida?</div>\n<div class=\"elementToProof\" style=\"font-family: Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\n<br>\n</div>\n<div class=\"elementToProof\" style=\"font-family: Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\nKas saaksite ka täpsustada, mida peate silmas \"avalikkusele suunatud infosüsteemi\" all? Küsin kahel põhjusel:</div>\n<ul data-editing-info=\"{&quot;applyListStyleFromLevel&quot;:false,&quot;unorderedStyleType&quot;:2}\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n<li style=\"font-family: Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); list-style-type: &quot;- &quot;;\">\n<div class=\"elementToProof\" style=\"margin: 0px;\">Koolide õpilaste nimekirjad ei ole enam avalikkusele kättesaadavad – sellest järeldaks, et ka Stuudiumi kaudu ei tohiks saada nime ja kooli seost kontrollida. On selge, et Stuudiumi kasutajad võivad olla nii\n koolide õpilastel, lapsevanematel, vilistlastel, õpetajatel kui ka muul personalil, kuid me ei ole teadlik ühestki põhjusest, miks samalaadse info avalikustamine ühelgi juhul tarvilik oleks.</div>\n</li><li style=\"font-family: Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); list-style-type: &quot;- &quot;;\">\n<div class=\"elementToProof\">On selge, et asutusesiseseks kasutuseks mõeldud funktsionaalsusel (sh sõnumid, failide jagamine jmt) on keerulisem kasutajate enumereerimist piirata – vajades kasutajakogemuse muutust, kuid ei tohiks olla võimatu! Et asutusesisesele\n isikuinfole pääseb ligi oluliselt piiratum hulk osapooli ja sellest tulenevalt on ka võimalikud ohud oluliselt väiksemad, siis hetkel on meie rõhk siiski avalikult kättesaadaval teabel (kuigi oleks kasulik ka mõelda läbi sisemise isikuinfo töötlemise alused).</div>\n</li></ul>\n<div class=\"elementToProof\" style=\"font-family: Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\n<br>\n</div>\n<div class=\"elementToProof\" style=\"font-family: Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\nKõike paremat</div>\n<div class=\"elementToProof\" style=\"font-family: Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\nGregor Eesmaa</div>\n<div class=\"elementToProof\" style=\"font-family: Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\n<br>\n</div>\n<div class=\"elementToProof\" style=\"font-family: Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\n--</div>\n<div class=\"elementToProof\" style=\"font-family: Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\n<br>\n</div>\n<div class=\"elementToProof\" style=\"font-family: Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\nHello!</div>\n<div class=\"elementToProof\" style=\"font-family: Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\n<br>\n</div>\n<div class=\"elementToProof\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\nThank you for pointing out shortcomings in our anti-bot detection!</div>\n<div class=\"elementToProof\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\n<br>\n</div>\n<div class=\"elementToProof\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\nAccording to EU General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR), personal data processing requires a lawful basis (<a href=\"https://eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-content/EN/TXT/?uri=CELEX:32016R0679#art_6\" id=\"OWAcbb393d3-828e-a29c-5518-ae273406a527\" class=\"OWAAutoLink\">Article\n 6</a>). Under which basis do you disclose/make available connection to a school (account existence) to unauthorised parties?</div>\n<div class=\"elementToProof\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\n<br>\n</div>\n<div class=\"elementToProof\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\nCould you specify, under which \"specific circumstances\" (\"teatud olukordades\"), are facts about account existence being available not a data breach? While certainly it may be available to school management, but did you also mean that parties unrelated to the\n school may check existence of accounts?</div>\n<div class=\"elementToProof\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\n<br>\n</div>\n<div class=\"elementToProof\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\nCould you also specify, what do you mean by a \"public facing infosystem\" (\"avalikkusele suunatud infosüsteem\")? Asking for two reasons:</div>\n<ul data-editing-info=\"{&quot;applyListStyleFromLevel&quot;:false,&quot;unorderedStyleType&quot;:2}\" style=\"text-align: left; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; flex-direction: column; display: flex;\">\n<li style=\"font-family: Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); align-self: start; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; list-style-type: &quot;- &quot;;\">\n<div class=\"elementToProof\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\">\nSchool student lists are no longer publicly available – this implies, that it should not be possible to check name and school connection through Stuudium. It is clear, that Stuudium accounts may exist for schools' students, parents, alumni, teachers, and other\n personnel, but we are&nbsp;not aware of any reasons, why making available similar information is necessary in any case.</div>\n</li><li style=\"font-family: Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); list-style-type: &quot;- &quot;;\">\n<div class=\"elementToProof\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\">\nIt is clear, that for functionality meant for internal use (incl messaging, file sharing etc), account enumeration is more difficult to limit – requiring changes to user experience, but should not be impossible! As institution-internal personal data is accessible\n by significantly less parties, and due to that, the potential risks are significantly smaller, our emphasis is currently only on the publicly available information (although it would be useful to consider the basis for internal personal data use).</div>\n</li></ul>\n<div class=\"elementToProof\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\n<br>\n</div>\n<div class=\"elementToProof\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\nBest wishes</div>\n<div class=\"elementToProof\" style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\nGregor Eesmaa</div>\n<div id=\"appendonsend\"></div>\n\n</body>",
